  - `POST /contao/venne-search/tag/assign` body `{ targetType, targetId, tagSlug }` → INSERT + Reindex der Page/File (async via Messenger, nicht blocking).
  - `POST /contao/venne-search/tag/unassign` body `{ targetType, targetId, tagSlug }` → DELETE + Reindex.
  - `POST /contao/venne-search/tag/bulk-assign` body `{ targetType, targetIds[], tagSlug }` → mehrere auf einmal.
  - `GET /contao/venne-search/tag/suggest?q=` → JSON `[{ slug, label, color }]` für Combobox.

